# Textile Shop — API testlar
# Payme kabinetiga endpoint: https://<DOMENINGIZ>/api/payme  (api prefiksi shart)

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Sog'liq
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/system/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Payme Merchant API (JSON-RPC) — kabinet va sandbox shu URL ga urinadi
# Authorization: Basic base64(MERCHANT_ID:PAYME_SECRET_KEY)
# Masalan: echo -n "your_merchant_id:your_secret" | base64
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payme
Authorization: Basic REPLACE_WITH_BASE64_MERCHANT_ID_COLON_SECRET
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "CheckPerformTransaction",
  "params": {
    "amount": 50000,
    "account": {
      "order_id": 1
    }
  }
}

###

### Payme — oxirida slash bo'lsa ham (301 bo'lmasin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payme/
Authorization: Basic REPLACE_WITH_BASE64_MERCHANT_ID_COLON_SECRET
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "CheckPerformTransaction",
  "params": {
    "amount": 50000,
    "account": {
      "order_id": 1
    }
  }
}

###
